>>>>>>> feature

Meaning:

<<<<<<< HEAD â†’ current branch code

======= â†’ separator

>>>>>>> feature â†’ incoming branch code

ğŸ”¹ Steps to Resolve a Git Conflict
âœ… Step 1: Open the conflicted file

Git will tell:

